RMB Fund   PORTFOLIO MANAGER
Todd Griesbach, CFA
Senior Vice President
Portfolio Manager, RMB Fund
×



Todd Griesbach, CFA
Senior Vice President, Portfolio Manager, RMB Fund
When Todd joined RMB in 2011, he brought 13 years of experience in analyzing equity securities and managing portfolios for mutual funds, institutions, and separately managed accounts. Prior to RMB, Todd worked as an equity analyst in Chicago for Columbia Wanger Asset Management and Ariel Investments. While rooted in value investing, his investment philosophy has developed and grown over the years to more fully encompass a “growth at a reasonable price” style. Todd is an alumnus of the University of Wisconsin-Madison, where he received a BA in Accounting and Finance and also a Master of Science in Finance. Todd was recognized with a Chartered Financial Analyst (CFA) charter in 1999 and is currently a member of the CFA Society of Chicago.
